            "body": "I think this is a bit of a weird place to \"validate\" VIMRUNTIME here as it is not really specific to lua. The problem could just as well manifest at the first time when wanting to load some .vim file. for the _startup_ part of #27527 , I'd rather add an explicit check as part of the startup sequence in `main()` (not sure where, maybe after initializing UI). ",
